# VSFTPD 2.3.4 Backdoor Exploitation Lab

## Objective
Identify and exploit a vulnerable FTP service in a controlled lab environment using Metasploit Framework.

## Lab Environment
- Kali Linux
- Metasploitable2
- VirtualBox

## Tools Used
- Nmap
- Metasploit Framework
- Wireshark
- Git/GitHub

## Enumeration

Performed service/version detection using:

```bash
nmap -Pn -sV 192.168.56.101
